{"tid":396470,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[定期開團］日本平價寵物用品代購","createTime":"2017-09-11T16:26:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T17:40:06.000Z","uid":135955,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c5bbbda093b3e197d5bc19acfa195fae97aa7646","tid":396470,"uid":135955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T16:26:01.000Z","msg":"工作關係 每一至兩個月就要去日本一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己本身有養寵物 見日本啲寵物用品唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但街鋪食水好深 網店又要等起碼兩星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以忽發奇想諗住幫各位巴絲代購日本寵物用品<br />\n<br />\n時間: 一至二個月 最少一次開團<br />\n(最近呢團13號前落訂 星期五即刻可以喺香港交收)<br />\n<br />\n交收方法：<br />\n早上九點至五點葵芳地鐵站<br />\n夜晚時段荔枝角地鐵站交收<br />\n(其他地點時間另議)<br />\n<br />\n平郵 掛號 同埋順豐都ok<br />\n<br />\n每樣嘢都係計返<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">7.3算匯率 加十蚊港紙手續費</span></span>(過重過大另議)<br />\n<br />\n有興趣嘅巴絲可以入tg group啊<br />\n平時傾寵物經都得啊！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/FEm0tkIWeltGsMc9SE0fzw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FFEm0tkIWeltGsMc9SE0fzw&d=vUg23RdbbGWRY1NFBUUeLgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=af43e146\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/FEm0tkIWeltGsMc9SE0fzw</a>"},{"pid":"912b114defdbc81596079affb258b91124b88dd3","tid":396470,"uid":135955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T16:47:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd34bdbf302d792b48466d83cf86c133ef413d94","tid":396470,"uid":70643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T16:53:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有意"},{"pid":"d88ad763028919f1fbd2cf15161e9cc21e897764","tid":396470,"uid